reviews.text: Prohibitively expensive if not a Hong Kong citizen.  Accommodation facility for family member non-existent nearby which meant they had to spend the night on a bench, or the staff did not help in suggesting places to stay the night. Very bad experience while here. Besides, this hospital could not treat me in heart diseases, and I requested transfer to a Shenzhen heart hospital who got me  well.
It is a rather good hospital
On Call 36小時 was filmed here

reviews.text: 最好就係唔用去見醫生 事實係好好 正如 今次因受不了服藥問題 改用咭針代替 哈 咁都得 在此謝謝北區醫療團隊好幫忙。鈣片的確難吞服。麻煩友係自已問題 。至此鬆口氣。開心到跳起。
地方寛拓,唯地下小賣部,收費高昂?何解!!!飱廳祗做職工膳食,外來顧客,拒與門外!!!離奇一室,外科同内科病人,混合其中?
只是一定要來才到而己
